        ->  Index Scan using idx_fk_inventory_id on rental r  (cost=0.00..1152.51 rows=15145 width=8) (actual time=0.008..0.063 rows=20 loops=1)
              Filter: (rental_date >= '2022-06-01 00:00:00+00'::timestamp with time zone)
